{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>起点与终点相隔4500米。现Charley 需要从起点骑车到终点。但是，他有个习惯，沿途需要有人陪伴，即以相同的速度， 与另外一个人一起骑。而当他遇到以更快的速度骑车的人时，他会以相应的速度跟上这个更快的人。先给定所有与Charley 同路的人各自的速度与出发时间，问Charley 以这种方式跟人，骑完4500米需要多少时间。得出的结果若是小数，则向上取整。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"Ride to Office ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出对应若干行数据，每行输出1个数，表示最快到达的时间。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入若干组数据，每组数据第一行n(1≤n≤10000),n为0，表示输入结束，接着输入n行数据，每行2个数据，表示速度v和出发时间t，如果t<0，表示陪伴人提早出发了。<p>","examples":"<input>4\n20 0\n25 -155\n27 190\n30 240\n2\n21 0\n22 34\n0\n\n</input><output>780\n771\n\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1227","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}